comment: American Horror Story has a hard time doing season finales, but Asylum is the exception. It's a fucking masterpiece - so beautiful, intense, and haunting.
From all the AHS episode... Let's admit it... Asylum's finale was A FUCKING MASTERPIECE
It's been almost four years, and this still gives me the chills.

“If you look in the face of evil, evil is going to look right back at you” 

Why tf is that so unsettling
HANDS DOWN BEST SEASON WITH A MAJOR PLOT TWIST.
